&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Gnosis&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Gnosis builds new market mechanisms for decentralized finance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Global interconnection has proved that open access to information, resources, and financial infrastructure is key for global resilience. By designing fairer marketplaces, Gnosis aims to build a more evenly distributed future. Our three interoperable product lines allow you to securely create, trade, and hold digital assets on Ethereum.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
