&lt;li&gt;Report high level insights to the rest of the team, based on data and user feedback, to support strategic decision making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support improvements to documentation and automation, in order to reduce the support load.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
